        #### NEW FORMAT OF PCR FILE ####
        The new FullProf .pcr format is expected. 
        Make sure that you have this format by using the FullProf toolbar: 
        
        	"EdPCR">>"output">>unclick"Classical Output Format for a Single Pattern in PCR".
        
